metadata.name: Rising Owl Society +18 #1
metadata.description: The Rising Owl Society is a collection of 6,666 ERC-721 NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain. We are primarily an art-focused project, however, Owls are wisdom creatures and they will do anything to make sure that their society is protected. The trait of an owl is inspired by art, history, and Secret Societies. For more info please visit the website.
